    Class and Description
    Attribute
    Attribute class to store related information regarding attributes in an arff file
    Class
    Class to store extracted information regarding predicted class from arff file.
    ClassFrequency
    This class discovers the majority class of the instances in the file.
    Rule
    Rule class that combines information from Attribute and Class to form a rule with antecedents and consequents
    RuleEvaluator
    The RuleEvaluator contains the mechanism that calls a Spark job to evaluate each rule against the instances of the dataset.
    RuleGenerator
    Class that makes the first pass through the file to generate list of possible rules.
